	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil habeo, quod modo ad te scribam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tantum, quia nuncius ille illuc abit, volui illi has ad te dare, ut tibi, si quid ad nos per ipsum mittere velles, certus daretur tabellarius.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde enim desydero tuas ingruentibus tantis motibus nec possum non<note type="margin">a.R.: non...? .. satis.</note> mirari, qui fiat, quod ita prorsus nunc sileas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> cum Mecardo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l28" cert="high">Basilęam</placeName> est profectus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rediit pridie; narrat <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlium</persName> per episcopatum <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basiliensem</placeName> suum militem ducere in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691" cert="high">Lotharingiam</placeName>, ut ibi se regis coniungat copiis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo sint proposito aut quid agant aquilonares, vel ipse nescit vel ego ab eo extorquere nequeo.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rumor est <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandum</persName> a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turca</placeName> inducias impetrasse; hoc si verum est, viderint nostri, quid agant.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostri homines (quod et prius scripsi) nimium ferociunt, et est magnum nobis modo cum illis negotium, ut ipsos cohibeamus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuo valde consulatum <persName ref="p2305" cert="high">Negelini</persName>, quem inibit sub festum paschae futurum.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus cohibeat illius spiritum et conatus, ut nostro contenti in domino tranquille vivamus.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Amen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Varia haberem, quę cuperem in sinum tuum effundere, sed literis commendare non ausim.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salvi sint fratres omnes, tum quoque domestici tui, quos ex me meisque omnibus diligenter salutabis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 26. martii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Ioannes Hallerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri suo colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingern</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
